Bismillahir Rahmanir Rahim. (In the name of Allah, the Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.) O Allah, send blessings upon Muhammad and the people of Muhammad. O Allah, protect us from all harm and evil, and inspire us to speak words that are truthful, and beneficial which please You. O Allah, Accept our supplication, have mercy on us, forgive us, and overlook our sins. Amen
